 *
 * Arguments:
 * 0: unit <OBJECT>
 * 1: position <STRING>
 * 2: vehicle <OBJECT>
 * 3: turret path <ARRAY>
 *
 * Return Value:
 * Nothing
 *
 * Example:
 * _this call FW_fnc_BPKCHST_UTIL_EHGetIn;
 *
 * Public: No
